seeker
======
A portable disk seek benchmark.

Usage:
sudo ./seeker.py /dev/sda


Example Results
===============
SSD results:
    Benchmarking /dev/sda [152627 MB]
    10000/2.42 = 4124 seeks/second
    0.24 ms random access time

HDD results:
    Benchmarking /dev/da0 [70007 MB]
    10000/60.26 = 165 seeks/second
    6.03 ms random access time


